--- .gitignore (原始)


+++ .gitignore (修改后)
```
# Dependencies
node_modules/

# Build outputs
android/app/build/
ios/build/
dist/
build/
target/

# Environment variables
.env
.env.local
*.env.*

# IDE files
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*.tmp

# Logs
*.log

# Python cache (if any Python files exist in project)
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd

# Coverage reports
coverage/
htmlcov/
.coverage

# Temporary files
*.tmp
*.temp

# OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Expo/EAS specific
.expo/
.eas/

# Supabase
.supabase/
```
